mint.filemakers.xmlMaker.structure
Class XsdTreeStructImpl

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      mint.filemakers.xsd.AbstractXsdTreeStruct
          mint.filemakers.xmlMaker.structure.XsdTreeStructImpl
public class XsdTreeStructImpl
extends AbstractXsdTreeStruct

This class overides the abstract class AbstractXslTreeStruct to provide a tree representation of a XML schema, with management of marshalling of several flat files to a xml file that respects the schema

Author:
Arnaud Ceol, University of Rome "Tor Vergata", Mint group, arnaud@cbm.bio.uniroma2.it

getValue

public java.lang.String getValue(XsdNode node)
get the value for a node

Parameters:
node - a node
Returns:
the value in the field associated to this node if the association exists (eventually replaced by a replacement value in a dictionnary), if not a automaticaly generated value if the node has been setted to request one, if not the default value if one has been associated to the node. Else return null
